Please, when reporting blocked streets, give the name of the post. We can then search for an official announcement of the blockage.
It's especially important if you cannot be bothered to zoom in and mark the point accurately. In most cases we don't know how accurate your marker is, so it's essential that you named the street. In this case, it's clearly obvious -- because you've marked a *building*, not a street.
